4],"tags":[416,308,465,50,114,144,31],"class_list":["post-13827","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-righteousness-al-birr","tag-agreed-upon-muttafaqun-alayhi","tag-chastity-al-husn","tag-good-deeds-hasanat","tag-humility-al-tawadu","tag-manners-adab","tag-modesty-al-haya","tag-virtue-al-fadail"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-3B1","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":107,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2010\/11\/10\/modesty-is-part-of-faith\/","url_meta":{"origin":13827,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Modesty: Do not admonish him, modesty is part of faith","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 10, 2010","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, passed by a man from the Ansar who was warning his brother about modesty, but the Prophet said, \u201cLet him be, for modesty is part of faith.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 24, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 36 Grade:\u00a0Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6302,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/12\/faith-branches-modesty\/","url_meta":{"origin":13827,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Faith: True Iman has sixty branches, including modesty","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 12, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cFaith has sixty to seventy branches, the best of which is to declare there is no God but Allah, the least of which is to remove something harmful from the road, and modesty is a branch\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17151,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/12\/haya-jannah-badha-nar\/","url_meta":{"origin":13827,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Haya: Modesty in Paradise, shamelessness in Hellfire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 12, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cModesty is part of faith and faith is in Paradise. Shamelessness is part of insolence and insolence is in Hellfire.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2009 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37590,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/12\/23\/salah-shoulders\/","url_meta":{"origin":13827,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Men covering shoulders during prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 23, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNone of you should perform prayer in a single garment that does not cover any part of the shoulders.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 359, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 516 Grade:\u00a0Muttafaqun\u00a0Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u200c\u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32083,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/14\/khuluq-islam-al-haya\/","url_meta":{"origin":13827,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Haya: Islam is characterized by modesty","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 14, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, every religion has a character and the character of Islam is modesty.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 4182 Grade: Sahih li ghayrihi (authentic due to external evidence) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5910,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/04\/iman-haya-together\/","url_meta":{"origin":13827,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Iman: Faith and modesty go together","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 4, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, modesty and faith come together. If one of the two is missing, so is the other.\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad lil-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1313 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0621\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/13827","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=13827"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/13827\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp